data.description: Cozy home in Ferndale! Two car detached garage, spacious patio, fenced-in yard for the animal lovers. Modern kitchen with granite countertops, oak cabinets, and newer major appliances (furnace, AC, hot water tank). Smart technology enabled (Nest, smart garage door & floodlights, ring doorbell). Incredibly spacious for the area and plenty of hide-away space. Located in beautiful & fun Ferndale and in walking distance of fun bars and restaurants. Downtown a short bike ride away!
